dc_description_s: This polygon shapefile depicts the Cowcod management boundaries based on California Code Title 14, section 150.06. This Conservation Area is part of the South Coast Study Region (SCSR). This Conservation Area was designated in 2001 after cowcod were declared overfished. This coverage displays the management boundaries of the California Cowcod Conservation Area for cartographic and illustrative use. California Department of Fish and Wildlife Marine Resources Region. (). California Cowcod Conservation Areas, 2003. California Department of Fish and Wildlife. Marine Resources Region. Available at: http://purl.stanford.edu/kv299cy7357. For current status of regulation, please refer to http://www.dfg.ca.gov. This layer is presented in the WGS84 coordinate system for web display purposes. Downloadable data are provided in native coordinate system or projection.
